data.text:
Delmarva Public Media is a local radio station service that operates in Salisbury, MD and Princess Anne, MD. They offer a variety of programming, including classical music, rhythm news, jazz, blues, and NPR news. With their offices located at Salisbury University and the University of Maryland Eastern Shore, Delmarva Public Media aims to provide informative and entertaining content to the local community.

WSCL 89.5 FM, WSDL 90.7 FM, and WESM 91.3 FM are the stations under Delmarva Public Media, each offering unique programming options. They also provide opportunities for community engagement through events and encourage support through donations and planned giving.
